          "reviewBody": "My daughter has been going to Elemenopy for 2 years. We absolutely loved it - the teachers are amazing- she always went in with a smile on her face. The timings excellent where the child is spending 2-3.5 hours in preschool. I have seen her develop, identify / analyse and make friends. One of the best part of the school is their App to communicate with parents - there they share photos of our little ones at school so we get to know what they are doing on a daily basis\n\nHighly recommend the school ! Thank you so much for all you’ve done for us ❤️",
